				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Project is not ~quite~ done yet, but this is where everything's been headed for the past 2 months.  Yes, it is possible to homebrew for the PowerGlove, thank you very much <img src="./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" />
<br />
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OlyE5zA4XZ4">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OlyE5zA4XZ4</a><!-- m --></div>

